\\	
\space 
\\
3^9 = 3^{1001_2} = 3^{1*2^0+0*2^1+0*2^2+1*2^3} = (3^{1*2^0})(3^{0*2^1})(3^{0*2^2})(3^{1*2^3}) 
\\ 
\space
\\
(3^{1*2^0})(3^{0*2^1})(3^{0*2^2})(3^{1*2^3})=(3^{1*2^0})(1)(1)(3^{1*2^3}) \tag{1}
